cmput301w15t07.TravelTracker.model

Class Receipt

  • java.lang.Object
    • cmput301w15t07.TravelTracker.model.Receipt

  • public class Receipt
extends java.lang.Object
    Model object for expense Item Receipt data. (i.e. image) Setters are not exposed - object attributes are set at construction time. This is so that mutations must be made at the Claim for observer notification and cache dirtying.
